  "title": "Myths of The Sea",
  "description": "Discover new mythological aquatic creatures, such as the Leviathan, the Kraken, the Hippocampus, and many more!",
  "body": "<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><img src=\"https://www.bisecthosting.com/images/CF/Myths_of_the_Sea/BH_Myths_of_the_Sea_header.webp\" width=\"1400\" height=\"451\" /></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">Myths of The Sea&nbsp;is a mod that adds mythical sea creatures to Minecraft, each with unique behavior and special item drops. Explore oceans and swamps to battle legendary beasts, tame aquatic creatures, and unlock powerful abilities through rare loot.</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 24px;\"><strong>Ready to play with your friends on the best hosting?</strong></span><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><br /></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><a href=\"https://bisecthosting.com/flashh\" rel=\"nofollow\"><strong><img src=\"https://www.bisecthosting.com/images/CF/Myths_of_the_Sea/BH_Myths_of_the_Sea_promo.webp\" width=\"1400\" height=\"251\" /></strong></a></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">I recommend <a href=\"https://bisecthosting.com/Flashh\" rel=\"nofollow\"><strong>Bisect Hosting</strong></a> for playing with friends because of their high-quality, lag-free servers. You can install any CurseForge modpack or your custom mods without errors. Plus, their support is available 24/7 to help with any issues. Use my code <a href=\"https://bisecthosting.com/Flashh\" rel=\"nofollow\"><strong>to get a 25% discount</strong></a> on your purchase.</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><img src=\"https://www.bisecthosting.com/images/CF/Myths_of_the_Sea/BH_Myths_of_the_Sea_description.webp\" width=\"1400\" height=\"151\" /></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">🦑 <strong>Leviathan</strong></span></p>\n<ul>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><strong data-start=\"461\" data-end=\"475\">Spawns in:</strong> Cold oceans.</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><strong data-start=\"492\" data-end=\"503\">Rarity:</strong> Very rare.</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><strong data-start=\"518\" data-end=\"529\">Health:</strong> 150 hearts.</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><strong data-start=\"545\" data-end=\"556\">Damage:</strong> One-hit kill on unarmored players.</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><strong data-start=\"595\" data-end=\"608\">Behavior:</strong> Extremely fast, strikes once then circles the player before attacking again.</span></li>\n</ul>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><strong data-start=\"687\" data-end=\"700\">🦫 Bunyip</strong></span></p>\n<ul>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><strong data-start=\"687\" data-end=\"700\">Spawns in:</strong> Swamps.</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><strong data-start=\"731\" data-end=\"742\">Rarity:</strong> Common (3&ndash;4 per swamp biome).</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><strong data-start=\"776\" data-end=\"787\">Health:</strong> 30 hearts.</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><strong data-start=\"802\" data-end=\"813\">Damage:</strong> 3&ndash;4 hearts per hit.</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><strong data-start=\"837\" data-end=\"850\">Behavior:</strong> Aggressive on sight, can walk on both land and water, very fast attack rate.</span></li>\n</ul>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><strong data-start=\"929\" data-end=\"947\">🐋 Bake Kujira</strong></span></p>\n<ul>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><strong data-start=\"929\" data-end=\"947\">Spawns in: </strong>Ocean coasts.</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><strong data-start=\"984\" data-end=\"995\">Rarity:</strong> Low (more common than Leviathan).</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><strong data-start=\"1033\" data-end=\"1044\">Health:</strong> 50 hearts.</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><strong data-start=\"1059\" data-end=\"1070\">Damage:</strong> 5&ndash;6 hearts per hit.</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><strong data-start=\"1094\" data-end=\"1107\">Behavior:</strong> Has a long cooldown between attacks.</span></li>\n</ul>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><strong data-start=\"1146\" data-end=\"1158\">🐟 Abaia</strong></span></p>\n<ul>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><strong data-start=\"1146\" data-end=\"1158\">Spawns in: </strong>Warm oceans.</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><strong data-start=\"1194\" data-end=\"1205\">Rarity:</strong> Frequent.</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><strong data-start=\"1219\" data-end=\"1230\">Health:</strong> 15 hearts.</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><strong data-start=\"1245\" data-end=\"1256\">Damage:</strong> 1&ndash;2 hearts per hit.</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><strong data-start=\"1280\" data-end=\"1293\">Behavior:</strong> Passive unless provoked, low damage output.</span></li>\n</ul>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><strong data-start=\"1339\" data-end=\"1352\">🐙 Kraken</strong></span></p>\n<ul>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><strong data-start=\"1339\" data-end=\"1352\">Spawns in: </strong>Any deep ocean.</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><strong data-start=\"1391\" data-end=\"1402\">Rarity:</strong> Very rare.</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><strong data-start=\"1417\" data-end=\"1428\">Health:</strong> 200 hearts.</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><strong data-start=\"1444\" data-end=\"1455\">Damage:</strong> Drains player life while grabbing.</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><strong data-start=\"1494\" data-end=\"1507\">Behavior:</strong> Aggressive toward nearby players, grabs and holds until enough damage is dealt.</span></li>\n</ul>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><strong data-start=\"1589\" data-end=\"1607\">🐴 Hippocampus</strong></span></p>\n<ul>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><strong data-start=\"1589\" data-end=\"1607\">Spawns in: </strong>Warm oceans.</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><strong data-start=\"1643\" data-end=\"1654\">Rarity:</strong> Uncommon.</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><strong data-start=\"1668\" data-end=\"1679\">Health:</strong> 45 hearts.</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><strong data-start=\"1694\" data-end=\"1707\">Behavior:</strong> Peaceful, flees when attacked. Can be tamed with raw fish and ridden to navigate oceans.</span></li>\n</ul>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">🧭 <strong data-start=\"1810\" data-end=\"1823\">Key Items</strong></span></p>\n<ul>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><strong data-start=\"1810\" data-end=\"1823\">Heart of Leviathan: </strong>Consumable that grants +2 hearts (up to 10 extra max) until death.</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><strong data-start=\"1922\" data-end=\"1940\">Bunyip&rsquo;s Fang:</strong> Used to craft fast-attacking claws (2 hearts per hit, dual wieldable).</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><strong data-start=\"2016\" data-end=\"2038\">Bake Kujira Bones:</strong> Used to craft bone armor with durability between iron and leather. Grants camouflage from undead mobs.</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><strong data-start=\"2146\" data-end=\"2164\">Tail of Abaia:</strong> Equip to greatly boost swimming speed.</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><strong data-start=\"2232\" data-end=\"2254\">Kraken&rsquo;s Tentacle:</strong> Equip to extend interaction range by 3 blocks.</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><strong data-start=\"2332\" data-end=\"2355\">Eye of Hippocampus:</strong> Used to brew night vision potions lasting 1 hour.</span></li>\n</ul>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><img src=\"https://www.bisecthosting.com/images/CF/Myths_of_the_Sea/BH_Myths_of_the_Sea_screenshots.webp\" width=\"1400\" height=\"151\" /></span></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/1271/853/myths-of-the-sea-3.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1920\" height=\"1080\" /></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/1271/858/myths-of-the-sea-8.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1920\" height=\"1080\" /></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/1271/859/myths-of-the-sea-11.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1920\" height=\"1080\" /></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/1271/863/myths-of-the-sea-2.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1920\" height=\"1080\" /></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/1271/864/myths-of-the-sea-3.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1920\" height=\"1080\" /></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/1271/866/myths-of-the-sea-11.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1920\" height=\"1080\" /></p>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://discord.gg/X4BEeSByGU\"><img src=\"https://www.bisecthosting.com/images/CF/Myths_of_the_Sea/BH_Myths_of_the_Sea_discord.webp\" alt=\"\" width=\"1401\" height=\"151\" /></a></strong></p>",
